X! Tandem directory
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is the directory where the X! Tandem search engine lives. More
information about the X! Tandem project can be found at:

http://thegpm.org/

----------------------------------------
Directions
----------------------------------------
1. Get the sources for X! Tandem.
2. Add any pluggable scoring modules you care to.
3. Run 'make' from <root>/src/.
4. Copy <root>/bin/tandem.exe to this directory.
5. It is a good idea to at least 'diff' <root>/bin/default_input.xml
   with the one found here, in case of any new changes.

